{"tid":880973,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"[全球航空應該全面禁12歲以下乘搭]獅子航空737客機折返不果墜毀","createTime":"2018-10-29T05:52:45.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-29T07:26:47.000Z","uid":65346,"like":0,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"435463048e20ad9b3248bdea34b324d95682455d","tid":880973,"uid":65346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T05:52:45.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20181029/58847948\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181029%2F58847948&d=qmI7%2FJfYZh2CmzOCciuMjLIOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=c70b6f5b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181029%2F58847948&h=21277948\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20181029/58847948</a><br />\n<br />\n【新增動新聞】印尼發生空難，廉航獅子航空（Lion Air）一班由耶加達往邦加檳的波音737 MAX 8客機，耶加達國際機場起飛後13分鐘失去聯絡，印尼當局證實客機已墜毀，當局指機上載有189人，包括178名乘客、<span style=\"color: red;\">1名幼童、2名嬰兒</span>及8名機組人員。以下是最新消息：<br />\n● 印尼財政部證實有僱員乘坐出事客機<br />\n● 印尼航空部門稱客機失事前曾要求折返，但未幾失去聯絡<br />\n● 當局指已在客機失聯位置以南約3至5公里發現客機殘骸，並發現手機、手袋等物品<br />\n● 中央社報道機上無台灣乘客<br />\n● 失事飛機8月才投入服務，飛行時數800小時<br />\n● 客機飛至5450呎上空急降 料殘骸處35米深海床（ <a href=\"http://bit.ly/2qe7Bym\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2qe7Bym&d=qmI7%2FJfYZh2CmzOCciuMjLIOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=a104619f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2qe7Bym</a> ）<br />\n● 客機乘客家屬趕抵邦加檳機場等待消息"},{"pid":"9a98f5bdc4dbe34322104c983fb6f0fff634fd7f","tid":880973,"uid":5267,"like":3,"dislike":8,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T06:15:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"89883fda3328b245a48cb872c8b802d646a31515","tid":880973,"uid":65346,"like":3,"dislike":10,"score":-7,"quote":{"pid":"9a98f5bdc4dbe34322104c983fb6f0fff634fd7f","tid":880973,"uid":5267,"like":3,"dislike":8,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-2